  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a stale-input-data weakener (W-EP-03): the primary blood rheology dataset carries a dataVintage of 2018-03-15T00:00:00Z, which predates the modelRevisionDate of 2026-01-10T00:00:00Z by nearly eight years. The narrative does not address re-validation against the updated model build, leaving an unacknowledged epistemic gap in input currency.",
